0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"上邊有冇睇曬樓主成篇野架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a52b11885aae5bab44a1e00a9f8c0f71749a50","tid":393081,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩訓左 乜釋放左劉霞喇咩？"},{"pid":"897700a3937dbf2a685f168fb28929c04747f4dc","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>too long didnt read.<br />\n反正我對自己思考能力有信心 無必要聽其他人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真 即是你嘅思考能力係既獨立且具批判性<br />\n你都應該係去了解其他人嘅睇法，咁先會更加豐富自己嘅思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果對方係錯誤嘅觀念，咁你就可以更加知道對手係錯緊啲乜，同時亦都可以補充自己嘅觀點<br />\n如果對方係正確嘅觀念，咁就可以睇下有冇啲咩可以自己參考<br />\n閉門造車係唔好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b0003283e1f4c735ab282934b181578aa03dfe","tid":393081,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮係咪冇睇內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a258e1b5a368ba6c5f061c0f19f507773ac0130","tid":393081,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔小心負評左<br />\nSor樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6462e64922de89429fe2e654ad3c177c29ab84","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上邊有冇睇曬樓主成篇野架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能大家都係好認同教育局教大嘅雙重標準同政治迫害"},{"pid":"fcd56293a63bf49f610fb7317ccc1aabaf3b5246","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩訓左 乜釋放左劉霞喇咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗未，因為政府各界都未發聲明譴責呢啲涼薄嘅行為，不過我相信既然政府各界咁痛恨過及妻兒呢種行為，遲早一定發表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48eb3e23091ebb82ee44b8fd8403ba10992e33d6","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔小心負評左<br />\nSor樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇所謂啦 負皮反而多人睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來發表呢篇嘢嘅時候，係打算吸引反對「禍及妻兒」言行嗰班人睇，比佢地睇下政府有幾咁雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c5dfcfdf23a6d1d3731cf88bcfaf3e68b7bdbf","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多負皮係咪冇睇內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能睇完都負皮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc03baeb616152a8c33fa0ed39bbabbc4e0b67","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"教大同政府各界要縱容嗰間學校縱容到幾時，說好的禍不及妻兒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147465e49668a37aa21ff880d81c2bca0fbef72e","tid":393081,"uid":103440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47c8781a5a8e0edadfa0898d167f62f0a9c6584c","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連狗都係垃圾之流，當笑話睇好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8852aed90a0510df6d6528425253c73dab5b9852","tid":393081,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"中國式的公民價值，不得連登仔說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p