T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會醒架"},{"pid":"1d1dd284dd24f3be17fc07e832ed8e5e12bf3e36","tid":393081,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"已block<br />\n同共狗殺人犯講價值都on撚鳩<br />\n左膠上腦"},{"pid":"12cded95cfcb2dbad88a59e2706c424f8be39d94","tid":393081,"uid":11840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"即係佢斷你子孫後代<br />\n都唔講得佢個仔？"},{"pid":"c205a3247bacc44192b8f8d881b230ed750263b7","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已block<br />\n同共狗殺人犯講價值都on撚鳩<br />\n左膠上腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好block啊，睇晒篇文先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddf1b9567beca52af14d1e6fe5f6a1423818e16","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地唔會醒架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b153425ee3f9bc0a568d9b8f7f1291321c5498b","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係佢斷你子孫後代<br />\n都唔講得佢個仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普世話，如果話嘅對象係政府就要落地獄，如果係平民就隨便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f3e1005eec937dfbd195461351185a7abaa2eb","tid":393081,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:41:38.000Z","msg":"唔可以淨係怪reader<br />\n篇文係寫得好有問題、難讀<br />\n先會咁多人解讀錯左"},{"pid":"01948ca7a4725b9137fc5dd00d7acb84f328bf9b","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以淨係怪reader<br />\n篇文係寫得好有問題、難讀<br />\n先會咁多人解讀錯左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁麻煩你指出咁問題所在喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又點樣改寫先容易讀"},{"pid":"ee5b8fd6709491e08695677bbd00c930932930d3","tid":393081,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"直得黎有D曲 曲得黎又曲唔哂"},{"pid":"3c9f74212eb7829d2c1761c93a8d5b44dcd26fcf","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我相信真係得<del>年份</del><span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span>呢度<em>有</em><span style=\"color: red;\">先會有人</span>認同「禍及妻兒」嘅言行係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有嘅事都<span style=\"color: red;\">應該</span>係<span style=\"color: red;\">由</span>始作俑者承擔， 唔應該連累佢身邊嘅人<br />\n呢啲咁簡單嘅常識你哋冇理由唔知道呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係琴日，我<del>見到</del><span style=\"color: red;\">對</span>呢個社會真係好失望<br />\n我見到竟然有學校對教大定係教育局發表聲明<br />\n「永不錄取教大畢業生同取消交大畢業生嘅intern」<br />\n呢種「禍及妻兒」嘅行動簡直人神共憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無法理解點解呢兩個學生嘅行為可以影響全校學生?<br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">對此</span>我深深感到恐怖，我好驚仔女會入到呢啲咁涼薄咁歹毒嘅學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我希望教育局同教大校委必須公開呢啲學校嘅姓名<br />\n並對佢哋強烈譴責甚至作出考慮殺校嘅處分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋呢個社會絕對唔允許有呢種咁超越人類道德底線嘅行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果教大校委同教育局唔作出任何行動，我好懷疑佢地係咪都係支持「禍及妻兒」呢種然後價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps.教大好似又出現「禍及妻兒」嘅橫額?我相信教大同政府各界應該已經召開記者會強烈譴責?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改左啲唔太通順嘅句子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會好讀咗啲?但意思其實冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">一切都係google錄音嘅錯</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f0c88e7b14f1fa8cc5de76c92756850e57e24e","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直得黎有D曲 曲得黎又曲唔哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，已經唔係好曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8e6cf35cdcf1275007be87bdb5900ffae810a6","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e133a1ccb8eb4203aff722cd0e9d702bcbb84fb6","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c33506d80cb0a41a636b6c411de37ef7707159","tid":393081,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔質素好低架咋<br />\n唔會睇得明曲線架喇"},{"pid":"bba1db2b3bdba52e52f40cbe7054e4abbe803ef2","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔質素好低架咋<br />\n唔會睇得明曲線架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係我寫得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd39a7e63eb141e89ee4a6eef43fd4c1193d1985","tid":393081,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"十卜樓主"},{"pid":"1e1b765b761f93414f4cb5574f859405c8efc3cd","tid":393081,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"認同禍不及妻兒o既, 唔該入一入黎, 有野要幫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/392168/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/392168/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7cfbd1ddc4f01bd9d6753251a3332f295c8b36b3","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十卜樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa8833cdffc0c23041ed3acae3301cd55b4ce4b","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同禍不及妻兒o既, 唔該入一入黎, 有野要幫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/392168/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/392168/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本政府好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔似香港政府及政府高官有免豁於禍及妻兒的權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20ec0fb2d34c6ae80fe1375317a52890118f1c7","tid":393081,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"一篇文引晒班係有熱誠但蠢既人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b880fd157815152b729e13098ea5ddbc5dd34f32","tid":393081,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"樓主你唔會叫得醒佢地架啦<br />\n<br />\n不過來來去去都係果一千幾百個超級盲反反上腦，但佢地白痴到以為自己係大多數<br />\n<br />\n其實成個社會笑緊連登高登出廢青就係咁解"},{"pid":"eafc244cd529281db9740303b9ffe019a3bc190f","tid":393081,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一篇文引晒班係有熱誠但蠢既人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}